        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. Phylogeny of NewWorld and selected OldWorld Ponera, inferred using the program IQ-TREE and 1,782 UCE loci.Node support values (ultrafast bootstrap/ SH-like) are shown when <100/100. Insert boxes are portions of phylogram expanded as cladograms." ;
